1. Navigated to my projects folder:
   cd "C:\Users\Reseanne\OneDrive\Desktop\New folder\alx_projects"

2. Created the repository directory:
   mkdir alx-intermediate-frontend
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend

3. Created the SASS setup directory:
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

4. Installed SASS version 1.77.4 using npm:
   npm install sass@1.77.4

5. Verified installation:
   npx sass --version
